cells.data: -- zipWith4 :: (a -> b -> c -> d -> e) -> [a] -> [b] -> [c] -> [d] -> [e]on zipWith4(f, ws, xs, ys, zs)	set lng to minimum({length of ws, length of xs, length of ys, length of zs})	if lng < 1 then return {}	set lst to {}	tell mReturn(f)		repeat with i from 1 to lng			set end of lst to |Î»|(item i of ws, item i of xs, item i of ys, item i of zs)		end repeat		return lst	end tellend zipWith4
